title: Command & Conquer: Generals 1.08 + Zero Hour 1.04
description:
Mount on Virtual Drive or Burn ISO Image to DVD5

Setup Contains Full Patched English Versions of Generals 1.08 and Zero Hour 1.08 + NOCD

And Many CD-Keys for Multiplayer (LAN, VLAN etc..) Gaming

Setup Contains Fixed Options.ini File For Generals and Zero Hour to Run This Game On Modern PC's.

To Run Game On x64 Systems: Turn Off in BIOS "Memory Remap Feature"

Installation: Run Setup.exe from DVD, Play

Good Game, Have Fun
